# IS2568 Artificial Intelligence Project

## Project Title
AI Prediction System: Football Match Prediction and Weapon Detection

## Project Overview
This project was developed as part of the **IS2568 Artificial Intelligence** course.  
The system demonstrates the application of both **Machine Learning** and **Deep Learning** through a web-based application built with **Streamlit**.

The application contains two main AI modules:

1. **Football Match Prediction** using Ensemble Machine Learning
2. **Weapon Detection** using Deep Learning with MobileNetV2

